sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Flutter Widget
    participant Notifier as Riverpod Provider
    participant Repo as Repository
    participant DB as Drift Database
    
    UI->>Notifier: ref.read(provider.notifier).addTransaction()
    Notifier->>Notifier: Set State = Loading
    Notifier->>Repo: insert(transaction)
    Repo->>DB: SQL INSERT
    DB-->>Repo: Success
    Repo-->>Notifier: Returns Result
    Notifier->>Notifier: Set State = Data
    Notifier-->>UI: ref.watch triggers rebuild
